These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, cycling, ice-hockey, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##2
6. the person who's sport is sailing is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | sailing | soccer     | ice-hockey | cycling |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, rock, techno
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, pony, frog, turtle
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
2. the owner of the turtle is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
5. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop    | techno     | rock  |
| Pet     | rabbit    | frog | pony | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, pop, rock
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, tea, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
2. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | pop   | house  | rock |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate | soy-milk | tea | fanta  |

