.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, dancing, fishing
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, car, roller, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person driving the roller##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | board-games | fishing | dancing  |
| Transport   | car  | skateboard   | quad-bike  | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, snowboarding, climbing
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, singing, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Sport   | biathlon    | rugby   | snowboarding | climbing    |
| Hobby      | hiking | drawing | singing       | woodworking |

