.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, tiparillo, prince, dannemann
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, roller, train, tram
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
2. the person driving the train is between the person driving the tram and the prince-smoker##2
3. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the train and the pall-mall-smoker##2
4. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Cigar    | pall-mall | prince | dannemann | tiparillo |
| Transport   | roller | boat  | train    | tram  |

