3. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the indian is between the french and the thai##2
5. the bolivar-smoker is the bolivar-smoker##1
6. the bolivar-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the thai##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | egyptian | thai | indian | french     |
| Cigar     | montecristo | game  | bolivar   | davidoff |

