.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, june, march, september
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, nigerian, russian
1. the argentine is on the right of the chinese##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is between the russian and the chinese##2
3. the person who's birthday is in june is the chinese##1
4. the nigerian is on the left of the chinese##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the argentine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Birthday   | april | june | march      | september   |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | chinese    | argentine | russian |

