3. the person driving the tram is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
6. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage       | juice | almond-milk | 7up    | tea      |
| Transport   | taxi       | tram       | snowmobile | skateboard |

