.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, jazz, trance, house
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, frog, hamster
1. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
2. the fan of country is the fan of country##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
5. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
6. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
7. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | country | trance  | house | jazz |
| Pet           | frog     | hamster | bird    | fish     |

