.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, cabbage, plum, potato
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, aconite, daisy, marigold
1. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating plum is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | cabbage  | artichoke | potato  | plum      |
| Flower    | marigold | poppy | daisy | aconite |

