.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-18::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, horror, satire, spy
City: edinburgh, marseilles, miami, berlin
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is the person traveling to berlin##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
4. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to miami is between the person watching spy movies and the person traveling to berlin##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | horror  | animation  | spy |
| City           | edinburgh    | berlin | miami | marseilles |

